title: 'Best quality product with elegant look .'
body: 'The media could not be loaded. Quality more than expectation. Leather and leaf quality are the best in market. No damage or tear. File was in a very good condition. Rings are metal and can easily hold upto 50 leaflets. Leaflets can hold a4 size or longer paper or certificates but laminated sheets need a bit trimming from sides before inserting. Out of 20 leaflets that were provided only 1 was defective. Rest everything is up to the mark. Overall great product. Go for it without any second thought.
